SELECT AD.UserTask.company, AD.UserTask.taskId, AD.UserTask.taskDate, AD.UserTask.depId, AD.UserTask.taskGroupId, AD.UserTask.taskCategoryId, AD.UserTask.taskActivityId, AD.UserTask.taskName, AD.UserTask.taskDescription, AD.UserTask.remarks, AD.UserTask.taskStatusId, AD.UserTask.refType, AD.UserTask.refNo, AD.UserTask.deadline, AD.UserTask.priority, AD.UserTask.projectId, AD.UserTask.sprintId, AD.UserTask.propertyId, AD.UserTask.costCenterId, AD.UserTask.empId, AD.UserTask.bpCode, AD.UserTask.bpName, AD.UserTask.parentTaskId, AD.UserTask.objId, AD.UserTask.objValue, AD.UserTask.dbTimeStamp, AD.UserTask.assignTo, AD.UserTask.scheduledTaskId, AD.UserTask.scheduleBases, AD.UserTask.scheduleFrquency, AD.UserTask.scheduleDate, AD.UserTask.createdBy, AD.UserTask.createdDate, AD.UserTask.assignedBy, AD.UserTask.assignedDate, --USER TASK LOG-- AD.UserTaskLog.taskLogId, AD.UserTaskLog.taskId, AD.UserTaskLog.taskLogTypeId, AD.UserTaskLog.filedName, AD.UserTaskLog.oldValue, AD.UserTaskLog.newValue, AD.UserTaskLog.comments, AD.UserTaskLog.createdBy, AD.UserTaskLog.createdDate, --USER TASK SPRINT-- AD.TaskSprint.dateFrom AS ADTasksprintdateFrom, AD.TaskSprint.dateTo AS ADTasksprintdateTo, AD.TaskSprint.sprintId AS ADTasksprintId, AD.TaskSprint.sprintName AS ADTasksprintName, AD.TaskSprint.subPageId AS ADTasksprintSubPageId, --USER TASK ACTIVITY-- AD.TaskActivity.subPageId AS ADTaskActivitySubPageId, AD.TaskActivity.taskActivityId AS ADTaskActivitytaskActivityId, AD.TaskActivity.taskActivityName AS ADTaskActivitytaskActivityName, AD.TaskActivity.taskCategoryId AS ADTaskActivitytaskCategoryId, AD.TaskActivity.taskGroupId AS ADTaskActivitytaskGroupId, --USER TASK Category-- AD.TaskCategory.taskCategoryId AS ADTaskCategorytaskCategoryId, AD.TaskCategory.taskCategoryName AS ADTaskCategorytaskCategoryName, AD.TaskCategory.taskGroupId AS ADTaskCategorytaskGroupId, AD.TaskCategory.carryActivity AS ADTaskCategorycarryActivity, AD.TaskCategory.carryStep AS ADTaskCategorycarryStep, AD.TaskCategory.subPageId AS ADTaskCategorysubPageId, --USER TASK GROUP-- AD.TaskGroup.taskGroupId AS ADTaskGrouptaskGroupId, AD.TaskGroup.taskGroupName AS ADTaskGrouptaskGroupName, AD.TaskGroup.depId AS ADTaskGrouptaskdepId, AD.TaskGroup.subPageId AS ADTaskGroupsubPageId, --AD DEPARTMENT-- AD.Department.depId AS ADDepartmentdepId, AD.Department.depName AS ADDepartmentdepName, AD.Department.active AS ADDepartmentActive, AD.Department.subPageId AS ADDepartmentsubPageId, --AD PROJECT-- AD.Projects.projectName AS ADProjectsprojectName, --AD Status-- AD.TaskStatus.taskStatusName AS ADTaskStatusName
FROM AD.UserTask LEFT JOIN AD.UserTaskLog ON AD.UserTaskLog.taskId = AD.UserTask.taskId LEFT JOIN AD.TaskSprint ON AD.TaskSprint.sprintId = AD.UserTask.sprintId LEFT JOIN AD.TaskActivity ON AD.TaskActivity.taskActivityId = AD.UserTask.taskActivityId LEFT JOIN AD.TaskCategory ON AD.TaskCategory.taskCategoryId = AD.UserTask.taskCategoryId LEFT JOIN AD.TaskGroup ON AD.TaskGroup.depId = AD.UserTask.depId LEFT JOIN AD.Department ON AD.Department.depId = AD.UserTask.depId LEFT JOIN AD.Projects ON AD.Projects.projectId = AD.UserTask.projectId LEFT JOIN AD.TaskStatus ON AD.TaskStatus.taskStatusId = AD.UserTask.taskStatusId
